snippet.title: Cannon Blast (Flash game 200?)
snippet.description:
The main player 'Pirate Pete' must defeat the invading Armada by firing canonballs and sinking all the enemy ships.
Use the up & down arrow keys to set the angle of the cannon and the space bar to fire.
